title: A Brony Tale - Original Soundtrack [iTunes]
description:
This is the official soundtrack to the new and highly anticipated Brony documentary "A Brony Tale". The soundtrack was created by Chris Kelly & Cayne McKenzie.

If you enjoy the soundtrack please consider purchasing it, or purchasing the documentary, to support the hard work of Brent Hodge, Ashleigh Ball, the film crew, and the entire Brony community.

More information about the film can be found at http://www.bronythemovie.com

All tracks are iTunes Plus quality: AAC 256kbps Variable
